	<p pid="b.205.5/1">The BBC has responsibility for the administration and enforcement of the television licensing system and TV Licensing carries out the day to day administration and enforcement as agent for the corporation. I have therefore asked the BBC's head of revenue management to consider the question raised by the noble Lord and to write to him direct. <a href="/pa/ld200506/ldlwa/51122wa1.pdf">Copies of the reply</a> will be placed in the Libraries of both Houses.</p>
</reply>
